        "black": true,
        "delay": 1,
        "dur": 1
      },
      "say": "把工作暂时交给了声望，外出寻找反击。既然她说要去演习海域，那她现在应该还在港口——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-1",
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "果然，在栈桥发现了正在眺望演习海域的反击的身影。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "指挥官？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "目光相对的瞬间，反击惊愕地瞪大双眼，但很快又恢复了一贯的笑容。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "嘿！指挥官，怎么能留下姐姐一个人工作，来这里偷懒呀？快回去快回去啦！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "反击似乎还是老样子。但既然已经注意到了她的反常，就得想办法弄清她的真正意图。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "这不仅仅是为了港区和声望着想，也是为了她自己。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "等等......这是要干嘛？靠太近的话，指挥官可是会掉海里的哦！啊哈哈……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "坚持着自己的想法，继续盯着她看。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "唉……我果然藏不住事……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "指挥官也真是的，好不容易两人独处了，为什么要浪费大好机会啊。",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "轻轻地碰了碰反击的手。反击瞬间吃了一惊，但马上又垂下头，撇开目光。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "终于，她喃喃说道——",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "…只要看到你们幸福，我就放心了",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "我又马虎又不善于思考，比起动脑更擅长体力活……就算想努力成为姐姐那样的人，大概也做不到吧…",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "比起我，当然是姐姐更适合陪在指挥官身侧……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "立马表示了否定。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "我……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "拿出了几张密密麻麻写满了字的纸，递到了她面前。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "那正是——和声望一起为反击制作的，秘书舰事务工作专用手册。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "指挥官和姐姐……亲手为我制作的手册？",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "准确的说，是由声望提案，自己给出创意，在反击至今为止所有努力的基础之上写成的。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "但是，为什么要做这些……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "say": "明明我都已经把姐姐叫来了。你看，有姐姐在，就能帮上指挥官更多的忙……",
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "声望在文书工作方面的能力明显优于反击。若只考虑效率的话，确实没有制作手册的必要。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "不过，并非任何事情都只有声望才能做得到。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "反击是秘书舰。而且，重要的是，我更希望声望和反击都能留在我身边。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "actor": 204020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "嗯……谢谢你，指挥官！ 很抱歉给你添麻烦了！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_outdoor"
    },
    {
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "反击擦了擦自己的眼角，笑了出来，脸上的表情，是比以往的任何笑容都要耀眼的真诚微笑。",
      "blackBg": true,
